title: No time like the present
text:
Seth Wenig Terry Collins, Matt Harvey 
New York Mets manager Terry Collins, right, talks with pitcher Matt Harvey during a workout at Citi Field, Wednesday, Oct. 7, 2015 in New York. The Mets will play the Los Angeles Dodgers in a National League Division Series starting Friday in Los Angeles.. (AP Photo/Seth Wenig) Posted: Thursday, October 8, 2015 11:18 am | Updated: 11:20 am, Thu Oct 8, 2015. 
NEW YORK — With a gaggle of watchful reporters waiting outside the Mets dugout and a row of photographers kneeling in position, Matt Harvey hopped up the steps and onto the field at exactly 10 a.m. 
Right on time.
